fields.physical_description: Design: floor game with hoops, mallets and balls
fields.title: croquet de salon
fields.history_note: Not strictly a table game but an indoor one to be played on a wood or carpeted floor.
fields.historical_context_note:
No. of Players: six or in pairs
Equipment required: 10 semi circular hoops with wood stands, 6 wooden mallets with a coloured band, 7 wooden balls, 6 wood pegs each a different colour, 2 wood poles marked as end posts
blue card box marked with the title and maker's initials on front in gold
pasted to the inside lid are the instructions in French; with typed English translation in box
